♪ Met a boy crazy for me ♪

20:24.139 --> 20:28.018
♪ Met a guy cute as can be ♪

20:28.101 --> 20:31.438
♪ Summer days drifting away to ♪

20:31.521 --> 20:33.857
♪ Uh-oh those summer nights ♪

20:33.941 --> 20:35.817
♪ Oh well-a well-a
well-a uh ♪

